
:name: NUCLEO_F401RE
:description: This script is prepared to run Zephyr on a NUCLEO-F401RE board.

$name?="NUCLEO_F401RE"

using sysbus

set zephyr_elf @/projects/playground/build/zephyr/zephyr.elf

mach create $name
machine LoadPlatformDescription @/projects/playground/bridle/samples/helloshell/renode/nucleo_f401re.repl
:machine LoadPlatformDescription @${CURDIR}/renode/nucleo_f401re.repl
showAnalyzer sysbus.usart2

macro reset
"""
    sysbus LoadELF $zephyr_elf

"""

runMacro $reset
